{"tid":2063972,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"來自美國的核爆 我什麼也不知道","createTime":"2020-06-14T12:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:47:42.000Z","uid":247923,"like":7,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"67bcc194f23988071052c22b114e87b037ff9765","tid":2063972,"uid":247923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"Beijing has prepared for two results of Hawaii meeting. The good one is Beijing successfully persuade US to ignore HK&lsquo;s issue. In exchange, Xi will give some substantial benefits to Trump, not only trade , even help him to win the election.<br />\n<br />\nThe bad one is the US government will refuse Beijing&rsquo;s gifts and insist its commitments to Hongkongers , hawk policymakers decide to sanction seriously Beijing if Xi do what they can't tolerate. The different result Beijing face, means Xi will take different actions on HK.<br />\n<br />\nWhat's interesting now is that the bars of tolerance from both sides had been reset this year, because of Coronavirus. Everyone saw how the White House and congress's attitude on CCP change during recent months. US can't directly retaliate China on virus problem because of lack of laws, but revenging emotion must be reacted on other issues, not only HK, but also HuaWei and Uyghurs."},{"pid":"f0c5dc6b82b4e022cc0014901e36a353afd0b111","tid":2063972,"uid":264245,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />source定老母"},{"pid":"e2529b6d58e6dcf929647be3e3e4ea70db204b0b","tid":2063972,"uid":247923,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"67bcc194f23988071052c22b114e87b037ff9765","tid":2063972,"uid":247923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"Beijing has prepared for two results of Hawaii meeting. The good one is Beijing successfully persuade US to ignore HK&lsquo;s issue. In exchange, Xi will give some substantial benefits to Trump, not only trade , even help him to win the election.<br />\n<br />\nThe bad one is the US government will refuse Beijing&rsquo;s gifts and insist its commitments to Hongkongers , hawk policymakers decide to sanction seriously Beijing if Xi do what they can't tolerate. The different result Beijing face, means Xi will take different actions on HK.<br />\n<br />\nWhat's interesting now is that the bars of tolerance from both sides had been reset this year, because of Coronavirus. Everyone saw how the White House and congress's attitude on CCP change during recent months. US can't directly retaliate China on virus problem because of lack of laws, but revenging emotion must be reacted on other issues, not only HK, but also HuaWei and Uyghurs."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"北京已經為夏威夷會議的兩個結果作了準備。 好的一面是北京成功說服美國無視香港的問題。 作為交換，習近平將為特朗普帶來一些實質性利益，不僅可以交易，甚至可以幫助他贏得選舉。<br />\n<br />\n 不利的一面是美國政府將拒絕北京的奉獻，並堅持其對香港人的承諾，鷹派政策制定者決定，如果習近平做他們不能容忍的事情，將嚴重製裁北京。 北京面對不同的結果，意味著習近平將對香港採取不同的行動。<br />\n<br />\n 現在有趣的是，由于冠狀病毒，今年雙方的寬容標準已被重置。 每個人都看到了最近幾個月白宮和國會對中共的態度如何變化。 由於缺乏法律，美國無法直接對中國進行報復，但必須在其他問題上回應情緒上升，這不僅包括香港，還包括華為和維吾爾族。"},{"pid":"57f79aa036c8f0a9e25b1e191ce360e261744042","tid":2063972,"uid":247923,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"quote":{"pid":"f0c5dc6b82b4e022cc0014901e36a353afd0b111","tid":2063972,"uid":264245,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />source定老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:30:50.000Z","msg":"來自地球"},{"pid":"da0bbc82a42ad65347dfecbe08a225b0fca939b6","tid":2063972,"uid":107297,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"甚至可以幫助他贏得選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntrust CCP? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6b8535a793cf1eecdc7ef220052b4a343c317c","tid":2063972,"uid":247923,"like"